{"tid":1832832,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺bnb俾人呃過","createTime":"2020-01-21T12:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T09:27:14.000Z","uid":42440,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dbe466c5558b8cb6ea1c1bad9d1e54ddf5d32779","tid":1832832,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:16:46.000Z","msg":"錯標題再開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n影到間屋鬼死咁靚<br />\n又有相話由間bnb睇晒成個城市景<br />\n點知原來只係俾個basement我，啲景又俾樹遮晒<br />\n樓上係個host住<br />\n<br />\ncontact個host for refund佢賴死唔認<br />\n去問customer service啦<br />\n吖屌你老味又話個host唔肯陪冇得搞，咁諗住算啦叫佢take down個host唔好俾佢再呃人啦<br />\n講講下屈返我俾錯誤資訊 sd晒相做evidence又話唔會接受<br />\n最撚好笑係叫我俾張喺host住緊嗰層嘅相嚟證明佢呃人<br />\n我咪投訴緊我唔係住嗰到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點俾佢<br />\n俾唔到佢就decision final唔再理<br />\n態度又閪 無啦啦close file <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncustomer service世撚界級<br />\n明明個ceo先前先話會verify 100% of listings<br />\n又話有問題bnb會refund 100%<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲以後去旅行book bnb小心啲<br />\n最慘係有起事上嚟個customer service會閪返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外想問下有冇巴絲有類似經歷 可以點搞<br />\nbnb唔同有線有得立嘢走上去話cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccf8e513ef216940cc948636bb8af9ed75ee341","tid":1832832,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"咩國家，舉報佢"},{"pid":"1971ae362185a3fe0456a85b2113846dd0b70b8a","tid":1832832,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ccf8e513ef216940cc948636bb8af9ed75ee341","tid":1832832,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"咩國家，舉報佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:28:16.000Z","msg":"挪威<br />\n點舉報 外國啲差佬唔係好hea唔理呢啲濕濕碎嘅案咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035fb84c786477e01a61f8ad69f19b4767f88864","tid":1832832,"uid":205